<br>
And don't let these guys fool yah: SCM is superior for AoE groups over SCF. :) Being able to consistently do 15% more nukage per mana bar and faster recovery between fights beats a sporadic on average 7% increase in damage per nuke imho :)<br>
<br>
I suggest (in the following order):<br>
<br>
1. SCM 3<br>
2. SCM 2 + MC 2 (saving up 6 points can be a long, lonely process)<br>
3. SCF 3<br>
<br>
I don't mean to knock anyone that likes the showyness of SCF. In the end, its a game, and you should do whatever makes the game more fun for you. And there are situations where SCF is superior (big mobs when the fight doesn't last long enough to use up all your mana; or Hail Mary finishing nukes where you pray you get a crit just at the right time). But from a purely numbers perspective SCM 3 is the way to go :) <p>Master Cydmab Promethean, Triune <BR>
Level 60 Arch-Mage, Morell Thule <BR>
